Support function to get unique set of scientific names

Source: R/get_animals.R
scientific_names.Rd

This function retrieves all unique scientific names

scientific_names(connection)

Arguments

connection

A valid connection to ETN database.

Value

A vector of all scientific names present in vliz.animals_view.
